channel.title: Can some one suggest something to me?
channel.description:
READ. please don't be afraid to read all of this. i know it looks like alot to read, but its not :D

so please......PLEASE (if that's not the magic word then the only other words i could think of are thank you and your welcome) help me out.
oh and btw... :eek: I HAVE BEEN LOCKED AWAY IN THE DOWNLOAD SECTION ALL LAST NIGHT!!! GOOGLE DOESN'T HELP AND NETIHER DOES YAHOO, ASK, SILABSOFT, OR google OR EVEN GOD HIM SELF( sorry bro...) :confused: help please... if you can. please :confused:
